{"tid":583543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[所...亂] 準新娘討「分手砲」　情夫做不下去竟挨告","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:47:29.000Z","uid":35468,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0be5ca6055af2399548ee7b7e9a90635aa8dc7a5","tid":583543,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"準新娘討「分手砲」　小王做不下去竟挨告<br />\n出版時間：2018/03/07 07:04<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180307/1309697/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180307%2F1309697%2F&d=rBBbksJCFdB8J9VfulbnZ5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6cd84e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180307%2F1309697%2F&h=ea10d716\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180307/1309697/</a><br />\n<br />\n準新娘向小王索「分手砲」，被拒後竟誣他性侵！<br />\n<br />\n今日出刊的《自由時報》報導，新竹準新娘小美(化名)在大喜之日前，想和王姓小王「發生最後一次」性關係，雙方在王男家中喝酒、脫衣、親吻後，小王想到小美即將嫁作人妻，一時心軟繼續不下去，小美自討沒趣，披上衣服就離開，王男一度沒穿衣服就追出去，想要拉回小美。<br />\n<br />\n小美羞憤之餘，竟向未婚夫陳男控訴王男試圖迷姦未遂，但檢方調查，小美與王男的LINE對話紀錄，2人間有大量如同情人般互相告白的對話，看起來2人正在交往；另小美於案發68小時候才到醫院驗傷，無證據可證明她當時陷於不省人事狀態，認定小美因不堪「索砲」被拒才憤而提告，將王男不起訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"2e0d1229e82c03b2e38a0d1f8b4fcc221ad79b97","tid":583543,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"所.."},{"pid":"9d9f81308dcea632ce60006956f0c492f9109e97","tid":583543,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"新竹 +1"},{"pid":"b881ea0e7c31a618ec3bd30eac23864ad50356e7","tid":583543,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8a339677db62e310688d19ac80404a29eb8502","tid":583543,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces